{"tid":227839,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"在飲食台留下我的遺書。。。。。。。。。。。。","createTime":"2017-05-03T13:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T12:49:02.000Z","uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09b11fc431311b5c0a49a2cc7c511f4a4b775546","tid":227839,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:01:19.000Z","msg":"&nbsp;&nbsp;我知道自己快要中毒身亡了。在動筆寫這封遺書前，我想了很久，遺書，其實要寫的是什麼？或應該問，遺書，其實是什麼樣的存在？我想，那大概是自己最赤裸裸的情感，是從出生以來最坦誠的話語。那是對神父懺悔也無法達到的程度，最真誠的文字。因此，我想，我的遺書寫的，是我對生命的遺憾、歉意及最後一絲的叮囑。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 首先，我要向所有曾經被我傷害的人道歉，或許是因為我的不成熟，或許是我的不經意，使你們受到傷害，真的對不起。我明白在我的人生中充滿了不足，充滿了缺憾，這些不足及缺憾經常傷害到身邊的人，我是明白的，但我還是奢望，在我離去後，你們都能給予我原諒。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 然後，是向我那深愛著的羊道別。我想，除了親人外，你是我人生中自己選擇的伴侶。我認為我們都是既保守又成熟的人，我們都明白「愛」需要付出，需要守候，亦因此，我們的關係能穩定地發展了四年多。對於不能實現我曾作出的許多許多不同的承諾，真是對不起呢！我真的要先走一步了。希望我們在一起的時光並不是白費的，我真誠地希望你並不會忘了我們這段美好的回憶，而是視這段回憶為美好的甜品，在日後遇上困難時就拿出來品嚐品嚐吧！最後一句，在我人生中能遇上你，實在太好了！<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 再者，是向我的家人感謝。感謝你們包容我這麻煩的存在，我明白我是多麼讓人煩擾，是你們給予我一個溫暖的家。感謝你們讓我讀hku <span style=\"color: pink;\">space</span>，讓我能過一個自己想過的大學生活。感謝你們支持我發展各種興趣，讓我的人生不至於枯燥無味。感謝，除此之外我想不到其他說話。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 最後，我希望大家要小心點刷牙，不要像我一樣，不小心吞下了牙膏，不然就要和我一起寫遺書了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada9563b845ff174dd127971228b86897df77664","tid":227839,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好唔死</span>"},{"pid":"b47b908d35dd5469e7a437a23227ab3f7d829a98","tid":227839,"uid":5667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:03:08.000Z","msg":"好行唔送<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c641686d158ccfb9d2ed0af280d56b29414bdb","tid":227839,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"呀b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160ee0fe84547e46b8195644e1f941776f2499e7","tid":227839,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8d1f6bd53730a685d120277be96884856a1838","tid":227839,"uid":9189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:37:57.000Z","msg":"羊B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09953fcf16cc1d77d6f0ba9d669ad237ba935bb8","tid":227839,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:48:28.000Z","msg":"快撚d死啦落雨親地淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43125663180e98d031071350922ef901fedd2ce","tid":227839,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:49:02.000Z","msg":"Tldr"}]}